6 AS INTRODUCED
7 An Act relating to vital records; amending 63 O.S.
2021, Section 1-321, as amended by Section 4, Chapter
8 87, O.S.L. 2022 (63 O.S. Supp. 2024, Section 1-321),
which relates to amendment of certificate or records;
9 prohibiting amendments to biological sex; and
providing an effective date.
